{"tid":826323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[IT救星]中銀一姐教你用金融科技識女仔","createTime":"2018-09-18T07:28:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T08:47:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e86ccea10dca77c8b67214b17251f6fec61de550","tid":826323,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180918/photo/bkn-20180918151140881-0918_00842_001_01p.jpg?20180918151149\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180918%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180918151140881-0918_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20180918151149&h=0340b200&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中銀香港一姐龔楊恩慈(Ann)竟然話「轉數快」其實係「識女仔大法」！<br />\n<br />\n話說「轉數快」最大特色，就係輸入對方號電話號碼或電郵地址，就可以即時跨行過數畀對方，相當方便快捷，最啱同朋友食完飯埋單夾錢！<br />\n<br />\nAnn向一位年輕男小記教路，可以主動話想轉帳畀心儀嘅女仔，咪可以趁機攞對方電話囉！<br />\n<br />\n雖然呢招都幾絕，但如果神女無心的話，畀個email就算，無謂畀個假希望對方！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180918/bkn-20180918151140881-0918_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20180918%2Fbkn-20180918151140881-0918_00842_001.html&d=wThkQtlCs4CCG4tZtdijlaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=32a0d300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20180918/bkn-20180918151140881-0918_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b15c129bae58ec7314a2564eb42674619d6f680","tid":826323,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:29:09.000Z","msg":"milf<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a51132030e2c3f7766f64446cb35f45a59e2b445","tid":826323,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T07:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e